OL,7,FCoronation Street fans watched
OL,8,Fmechanic Tyrone suffer a spinal cord
OL,9,Finjury in a hit and run, leaving him
OL,10,Funable to walk.
OL,12,F"I'm so impressed that Coronation
OL,13,FStreet has chosen to tell this
OL,14,Fimportant story," Mr Hibbert, who is
OL,15,Fthe vice president of the Spinal
OL,16,FInjuries Association, said.
