OL,3,CManchester bomb survivor tells
OL,4,CCoronation Street stars about life
OL,5,Cafter injury
OL,7,FMr Hibbert was among those standing
OL,8,Fclosest to attacker Salman Abedi when
OL,9,Fhe detonated the homemade rucksack
OL,10,Fbomb at the Ariana Grande concert in
OL,11,FMay 2017 ` killing 22 people and
OL,12,Finjuring hundreds more.
OL,14,FHe suffered 22 shrapnel wounds and
OL,15,Frequired life-saving surgery at
OL,16,FSalford Royal Hospital. His spine was
OL,17,Fsevered by shrapnel, leaving him with
OL,18,Fa T10 complete spinal cord injury and
OL,19,Fparalysed from the waist down.
