OL,3,CManchester bomb survivor tells
OL,4,CCoronation Street stars about life
OL,5,Cafter injury
OL,7,F"Spinal cord injury can happen to
OL,8,Fanyone, at any time, and having such a
OL,9,Fbig TV programme shine a light on the
OL,10,Frealities of living with it will make
OL,11,Fa huge difference," Mr Hibbert added.
OL,13,F"By showing that ordinary people can
OL,14,Fbe affected, it helps to raise
OL,15,Fawareness, break down barriers and
OL,16,Fstart vital conversations about life
OL,17,Fafter injury.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@SO]uD@AOU
