OL,3,CManchester bomb survivor tells
OL,4,CCoronation Street stars about life
OL,5,Cafter injury
OL,7,F"It was an honour for Gabby and I to
OL,8,Fshare our experience and see first-
OL,9,Fhand the care and respect the team are
OL,10,Fputting into getting this right."
OL,12,FThe Coronation Street research team
OL,13,Fworked with the Spinal Injuries
OL,14,FAssociation in developing Tyrone's
OL,15,Fstoryline, and the charity advised
OL,16,Fwriters on scripts, ITV said.
