OL,3,CManchester bomb survivor tells
OL,4,CCoronation Street stars about life
OL,5,Cafter injury
OL,7,F"We might be telling this story on
OL,8,Fscreen but at the end of the day we go
OL,9,Fhome to our family and friends and
OL,10,Fleave behind what the characters are
OL,11,Fgoing through," Mr Halsall said.
OL,13,F"Even just trying to negotiate getting
OL,14,Fround the set in the wheelchair has
OL,15,Fbeen a real eyeopener for me, so to
OL,16,Fhear Martin's own stories about how
OL,17,Fhis life has changed has been really
OL,18,Fhelpful and also humbling."
